Q: What is sanity?
<br>A: Sanity is when the mind sees the truth and not any kind of illusions.
<br>Q: Is insanity caused by samskaras?
<br>A: In the world, everything is the result of samskaras. We feel we are sane, but those who are more knowledgeable think we are insane. So comparatively all are insane except God. <span class=date>3/30/80</span>
